# Sample OAuth2 spring boot app
Demo app that authenticates its users against an OAuth2 provider. It uses Spring Boot and Spring Security OAuth2 on the back end.

## Requirement
- Create an OAuth2 App. The redirect uri must end with /login 

## Configure
All configuration for this app is located in application.properties. Locate and configure the following parameters:
- client-id
- client-secret
- scope
- authorization-endpoint-uri
- token-endpoint-uri
- userinfo-endpoint-uri

## Compile and deploy
mvn clean package

## Run as spring boot app
mvn spring-boot:run


